HEADWORD: innumerate
<hw>innumerate</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Lacking knowledge and
understanding of mathematical concepts and methods; by analogy with
<contr>illiterate</contr>. Opposite of <ant>numerate</ant>.</def>
<see>Also See: <er>educated</er>; <er>illiterate</er>.</see>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Innumerous</ent>⟦br⟧
